00:10:38.480 --> 00:10:41.030
me.

00:10:41.040 --> 00:10:44.790
What if

00:10:44.790 --> 00:10:44.800
Kamala

00:10:44.800 --> 00:10:48.389
Harris is with Hillary?

00:10:48.399 --> 00:10:50.389
Because Hillary came out immediately

00:10:50.399 --> 00:10:54.470
with Bill and endorsed Kamala Harris.

00:10:54.480 --> 00:10:57.110
Then Joe—from what I understand,

00:10:57.120 --> 00:10:59.110
people are telling me that Barack

00:10:59.120 --> 00:11:01.350
Obama said, "No, not so

00:11:01.360 --> 00:11:03.829
fast. This has to be voted on

00:11:03.839 --> 00:11:06.949
at the Democratic caucus."Well, if

00:11:06.959 --> 00:11:09.829
she ends up taking

00:11:09.829 --> 00:11:09.839
it—if

00:11:09.839 --> 00:11:11.269
she doesn't take it and they don't get

00:11:11.279 --> 00:11:13.750
her in—is he planning to do something

00:11:13.760 --> 00:11:16.870
with

00:11:16.880 --> 00:11:22.870
Kamala?

00:11:22.880 --> 00:11:25.509
Is he planning to do something with

00:11:25.519 --> 00:11:28.790
Michelle and maybe Gavin in the future?

00:11:28.800 --> 00:11:31.269
I don't know. But I've told you all I've

00:11:31.279 --> 00:11:33.670
prayed over that for over

00:11:33.680 --> 00:11:36.550
two years now,

00:11:36.560 --> 00:11:40.069
that I saw her running with Gavin.

00:11:40.079 --> 00:11:43.190
They were a force to be reckoned

00:11:43.200 --> 00:11:44.949
with. People

00:11:44.959 --> 00:11:46.630
go, "Well, it's a

00:11:46.630 --> 00:11:46.640
shoo-in."No.

00:11:46.640 --> 00:11:48.870
If Michelle and Gavin go, it

00:11:48.880 --> 00:11:51.350
is. We've got to pray. It's like some

00:11:51.360 --> 00:11:52.550
people say, "Well, we've got a little

00:11:52.560 --> 00:11:54.389
bit of victory here, and we can see the

00:11:54.399 --> 00:11:56.230
finish line."It's like the

00:11:56.240 --> 00:11:58.230
tortoise and the hare. The hare goes,

00:11:58.240 --> 00:12:00.150
"Man, I've got this race,"and he goes

00:12:00.160 --> 00:12:01.910
over there and he lays down and takes

00:12:01.920 --> 00:12:04.150
a nap because he thinks he can beat that

00:12:04.160 --> 00:12:06.310
tortoise. And the tortoise is going, "I

00:12:06.320 --> 00:12:07.670
think I can. I think I

00:12:07.680 --> 00:12:10.150
can."He's

00:12:10.160 --> 00:12:11.910
tripping over himself and he's

00:12:11.920 --> 00:12:13.590
falling, and the hare is over there

00:12:13.600 --> 00:12:15.910
sleeping. All of a sudden, the

00:12:15.920 --> 00:12:18.870
tortoise gets ahead of the

00:12:18.870 --> 00:12:18.880
hare,

00:12:18.880 --> 00:12:20.790
and the whole story

00:12:20.790 --> 00:12:20.800
everyone

00:12:20.800 --> 00:12:23.509
knows: the tortoise wins and the

00:12:23.509 --> 00:12:23.519
hare

00:12:23.519 --> 00:12:26.629
loses because he got overconfident in

00:12:26.639 --> 00:12:29.430
his ability to win.

00:12:29.440 --> 00:12:31.910
Do not let your guard down

00:12:31.920 --> 00:12:34.550
spiritually just because you think we

00:12:34.560 --> 00:12:37.910
have won. We have got to take the enemy

00:12:37.920 --> 00:12:42.470
camp seriously. And I'm not calling

00:12:42.480 --> 00:12:45.030
the Democrats the enemy; I'm

00:12:45.040 --> 00:12:46.790
talking about the principalities and

00:12:46.800 --> 00:12:49.030
powers and the rulers over the darkness

00:12:49.040 --> 00:12:50.710
and spiritual wickedness in high

00:12:50.720 --> 00:12:53.269
places. We wrestle not against flesh and

00:12:53.279 --> 00:12:55.190
blood, ladies and gentlemen, but against

00:12:55.200 --> 00:12:57.670
those things. The Bible's told us that.

00:12:57.680 --> 00:13:00.150
So, I never label a human being as an

00:13:00.160 --> 00:13:02.629
enemy, ever. But I'm talking about the

00:13:02.639 --> 00:13:04.310
demonic forces right now. That's what

00:13:04.320 --> 00:13:07.190
I'm trying to say. Never let your guard

00:13:07.200 --> 00:13:10.389
down on your enemy, ever. That's the

00:13:10.399 --> 00:13:13.030
devil. He has a plan to kill,

00:13:13.040 --> 00:13:15.750
steal, and destroy. But the Bible says

00:13:15.760 --> 00:13:17.670
that Jesus came that we might have life

00:13:17.680 --> 00:13:19.829
and life more abundantly. I'm just

00:13:19.839 --> 00:13:25.030
saying a lot of the theologies

00:13:25.040 --> 00:13:28.790
line up with

00:13:28.800 --> 00:13:31.750
the dark side. And I'm not saying all

00:13:31.760 --> 00:13:34.310
the Republican side is always light,

00:13:34.320 --> 00:13:36.949
but they have a tendency to sway good.

00:13:36.959 --> 00:13:40.069
Never stop and be the hare laying down

00:13:40.079 --> 00:13:43.030
so the tortoise can win. Even when we

00:13:43.040 --> 00:13:44.949
have the upper hand spiritually and we

00:13:44.959 --> 00:13:47.269
see that victory

00:13:47.279 --> 00:13:49.350
finish line, don't

00:13:49.360 --> 00:13:54.790
let your guard down. I always

00:13:54.790 --> 00:13:54.800
say—this

00:13:54.800 --> 00:13:56.310
is going to be a gross

00:13:56.310 --> 00:13:56.320
illustration—but

00:13:56.320 --> 00:13:57.750
it's like an old dead

00:13:57.760 --> 00:13:59.670
dog in the road. You keep running it

00:13:59.680 --> 00:14:03.110
over until it's a greasy spot.

00:14:03.110 --> 00:14:03.120
You've

00:14:03.120 --> 00:14:06.150
got to

00:14:06.160 --> 00:14:08.230
keep going over it. That's probably a

00:14:08.240 --> 00:14:10.550
gross illustration, but you keep hitting

00:14:10.560 --> 00:14:12.790
that devil until he's a greasy spot.

00:14:12.800 --> 00:14:15.750
Don't give up when you see the

00:14:15.760 --> 00:14:18.150
first blade of your miracle. You need

00:14:18.160 --> 00:14:19.910
the blade, then the ear, then

00:14:19.920 --> 00:14:21.590
the full manifestation of the

00:14:21.600 --> 00:14:24.790
whole fruit of the corn. Do not

00:14:24.800 --> 00:14:27.829
give up on this. It's time for us to put

00:14:27.839 --> 00:14:30.470
our

00:14:30.480 --> 00:14:33.430
shields up even stronger and stand up

00:14:33.440 --> 00:14:35.670
even greater than what we ever had

00:14:35.680 --> 00:14:37.910
before, believing for a turnaround of

00:14:37.920 --> 00:14:40.550
our nation, to believe for things to get

00:14:40.560 --> 00:14:43.350
better and not worse. It's time to

00:14:43.360 --> 00:14:45.829
believe even greater.

00:14:45.839 --> 00:14:48.710
Put the

00:14:48.720 --> 00:14:50.629
big boys up on the front line of that

00:14:50.639 --> 00:14:52.230
football team. It's time to

00:14:52.240 --> 00:14:54.230
put the great defensive backs up

00:14:54.240 --> 00:14:55.509
there going, "Hey, we're going to stop

00:14:55.519 --> 00:14:57.269
the run, and

00:14:57.279 --> 00:14:58.790
they're not going to get the

00:14:58.790 --> 00:14:58.800
touchdown."That's

00:14:58.800 --> 00:15:01.110
what you've got to do.

00:15:01.120 --> 00:15:02.550
I probably kicked that too

00:15:02.560 --> 00:15:05.509
much, but that's why I

00:15:05.519 --> 00:15:07.350
just feel in my spirit to tell you all

00:15:07.360 --> 00:15:09.030
it's not time to stop. It's not time to

00:15:09.040 --> 00:15:10.790
give up.

00:15:10.800 --> 00:15:15.030
It's time to press.

00:15:15.040 --> 00:15:16.710
I warned you about that. So go

00:15:16.720 --> 00:15:19.590
watch that video of that

00:15:19.590 --> 00:15:19.600
covered

00:15:19.600 --> 00:15:22.069
wagon

00:15:22.079 --> 00:15:24.230
dream that he had. It will bless you.

00:15:26.240 --> 00:15:27.910
It's going to make you go, "Oh my

00:15:27.920 --> 00:15:30.790
gosh, look at where we are."But look at

00:15:30.800 --> 00:15:33.750
what he says afterward. After the

00:15:33.760 --> 00:15:37.110
election, there was a flash. And he

00:15:37.120 --> 00:15:38.629
talked about this. He said, "I saw a

00:15:38.639 --> 00:15:40.629
flash, and everybody was dazed and

00:15:40.629 --> 00:15:40.639
confused."He

00:15:40.639 --> 00:15:43.430
warned everybody. He

00:15:43.440 --> 00:15:45.030
said everybody was dazed and confused, and

00:15:45.040 --> 00:15:47.590
everybody was on the East

00:15:47.590 --> 00:15:47.600
Coast—they

00:15:47.600 --> 00:15:49.590
were all in like cots, and

00:15:49.600 --> 00:15:52.230
they were all trying to find shelter and

00:15:52.240 --> 00:15:54.389
food and all kinds of stuff. What

00:15:54.399 --> 00:15:56.629
happens? I'm

00:15:56.639 --> 00:15:58.710
telling you all, the Lord has warned me

00:15:58.720 --> 00:16:01.110
there's a storm coming. I've told you

00:16:01.120 --> 00:16:03.189
all countless times the Lord has

00:16:03.199 --> 00:16:05.430
warned me there's a storm coming. What

00:16:05.440 --> 00:16:08.470
is Dana Coverstone? He doesn't directly

00:16:08.480 --> 00:16:10.150
say it, but he's kind of insinuating

00:16:10.160 --> 00:16:11.910
something. I saw the short-haired

00:16:11.910 --> 00:16:11.920
blonde-headed

00:16:11.920 --> 00:16:13.990
lady. So that's a

00:16:14.000 --> 00:16:15.030
little recap. I saw the short

00:16:15.030 --> 00:16:15.040
blonde-headed

00:16:15.040 --> 00:16:17.910
lady with Kamala Harris. So

00:16:17.920 --> 00:16:21.110
if we see all this stuff panning out,

00:16:22.480 --> 00:16:24.629
it looks like that vision, everything I

00:16:24.639 --> 00:16:26.790
saw again. It looks like I hit it right

00:16:26.800 --> 00:16:28.069
on the head. Let's just see. We'll see

00:16:28.079 --> 00:16:29.749
how it pans out.

00:16:36.959 --> 00:16:38.790
They're all going

00:16:38.800 --> 00:16:40.389
and they're happening almost like

00:16:40.399 --> 00:16:41.910
dominoes. Everything that the Lord

00:16:41.920 --> 00:16:43.749
showed me about Joe Biden being removed,

00:16:43.759 --> 00:16:45.670
I warned you all was coming and it

00:16:45.680 --> 00:16:48.629
happened. I said he

00:16:48.639 --> 00:16:50.550
will not even be running. It will not

00:16:50.560 --> 00:16:54.230
happen. I told you this last year,

00:16:54.240 --> 00:16:58.790
2023. I warned you in September of 2023.

00:16:58.800 --> 00:17:01.670
I told you this was coming. I

00:17:01.680 --> 00:17:03.350
