00:17:08.480 --> 00:17:10.870
So, I was seeing in the future what

00:17:10.880 --> 00:17:13.029
the Lord was telling me was coming, but

00:17:13.039 --> 00:17:16.309
I thought that it was coming that year.

00:17:16.319 --> 00:17:18.949
But no, it's almost a whole year later

00:17:18.949 --> 00:17:18.959
from

00:17:18.959 --> 00:17:20.870
what I saw in the spirit.

00:17:20.880 --> 00:17:22.470
I thought this was imminent. That's why I

00:17:22.480 --> 00:17:23.909
thought it was imminent; I felt it

00:17:23.919 --> 00:17:26.630
inside. This is what's going to happen

00:17:26.640 --> 00:17:29.590
this month, this next month. I

00:17:29.600 --> 00:17:31.029
even told my son, "We're going to have

00:17:31.039 --> 00:17:32.789
an October surprise."Well, we did have

00:17:32.799 --> 00:17:35.110
an October surprise for Israel. It was

00:17:35.120 --> 00:17:36.549
what the Lord was showing me. I prayed

00:17:36.559 --> 00:17:37.669
over it and the Lord told me there's

00:17:37.679 --> 00:17:39.029
going to be a serious event take

00:17:39.039 --> 00:17:40.310
place. I thought it was about

00:17:40.320 --> 00:17:42.789
America, but I was interceding for

00:17:42.799 --> 00:17:44.470
Israel and what happened on the

00:17:44.480 --> 00:17:47.029
Sabbath. It was a tragic thing that

00:17:47.039 --> 00:17:49.190
happened for all those people that were

00:17:49.190 --> 00:17:49.200
dragged

00:17:49.200 --> 00:17:50.549
and murdered and everything.

00:17:50.559 --> 00:17:54.070
It was terrible. I was

00:17:54.080 --> 00:17:56.310
interceding for that. But like I said,

00:17:56.320 --> 00:17:58.710
it's growing in your gifting; it's

00:17:58.720 --> 00:18:01.110
growing in what God's called you to do.

00:18:01.120 --> 00:18:03.750
I'm not perfect. I'm learning just

00:18:03.760 --> 00:18:06.310
like you all. I'm learning how to flow

00:18:06.320 --> 00:18:08.470
in the gift that God has given me.

00:18:08.480 --> 00:18:10.789
It takes practice. It takes time. It

00:18:10.799 --> 00:18:13.190
takes maturity. And it's a day-to-day

00:18:13.200 --> 00:18:15.830
process. Just like how a baby learns

00:18:15.840 --> 00:18:19.590
to walk and pull itself up

00:18:19.600 --> 00:18:22.070
and crawl and walk and then run and

00:18:22.080 --> 00:18:23.590
fall. They keep falling. You learn.

00:18:23.600 --> 00:18:24.950
That's how you learn spiritually. You

00:18:24.960 --> 00:18:26.230
just keep picking yourself up. You

00:18:26.240 --> 00:18:27.909
learn. And that's how we process

00:18:27.919 --> 00:18:30.230
things. So, like I said, this is

00:18:30.240 --> 00:18:31.669
how I've

00:18:31.679 --> 00:18:32.870
learned over the course of the years

00:18:32.880 --> 00:18:35.510
I've done things. I just want to

00:18:35.520 --> 00:18:37.990
encourage you all that good days are

00:18:38.000 --> 00:18:40.070
happening for the body of Christ. Good

00:18:40.080 --> 00:18:42.070
days are happening for the people who

00:18:42.080 --> 00:18:44.150
will believe him for miracles, signs,

00:18:44.160 --> 00:18:46.470
and wonders in these last days. This is

00:18:46.480 --> 00:18:48.870
not a time to bury our head in the

00:18:48.880 --> 00:18:51.029
sand like an ostrich and say, "Well, I

00:18:51.039 --> 00:18:52.470
don't want to know anything more that's

00:18:52.470 --> 00:18:52.480
coming."I

00:18:52.480 --> 00:18:54.150
try to warn you of these

00:18:54.160 --> 00:18:55.029
things. They said, "What are you

00:18:55.039 --> 00:18:56.150
telling us all this stuff for? We don't

00:18:56.160 --> 00:18:57.190
want to hear about the plague that's

00:18:57.200 --> 00:18:59.750
going to kill 350 million

00:18:59.750 --> 00:18:59.760
people,"because

00:18:59.760 --> 00:19:02.470
I believe we can lessen it. I believe we

00:19:02.480 --> 00:19:05.669
can maybe even stop it altogether. I

00:19:05.679 --> 00:19:07.909
warned you all that we have power and

00:19:07.919 --> 00:19:10.390
authority. If the Lord would have

00:19:10.400 --> 00:19:13.590
mercy on Sodom and Gomorrah for

00:19:13.590 --> 00:19:13.600
ten

00:19:13.600 --> 00:19:16.710
righteous people,

00:19:16.720 --> 00:19:18.789
and he said he would

00:19:18.799 --> 00:19:22.390
spare the city. He would spare them.

00:19:22.400 --> 00:19:25.669
When Abraham was interceding for

00:19:25.679 --> 00:19:29.669
that city, how much more with a new

00:19:29.679 --> 00:19:32.870
covenant with his son that we have as

00:19:32.880 --> 00:19:36.870
believers? If there's 50,000 righteous in

00:19:36.880 --> 00:19:39.590
this nation in America or all around the

00:19:39.600 --> 00:19:42.630
world asking God for him to

00:19:42.640 --> 00:19:45.750
step in and intervene, how much more

00:19:45.760 --> 00:19:48.150
would Jesus want to do it for us as

00:19:48.160 --> 00:19:51.510
blood-washed,

00:19:51.510 --> 00:19:51.520
born-again

00:19:51.520 --> 00:19:54.310
children of the most high God? How much

00:19:54.320 --> 00:19:57.909
more would he want to step in for us

00:19:57.919 --> 00:19:59.909
if he would do it for Abraham and he

00:19:59.919 --> 00:20:03.350
called him a friend of God?

00:20:03.360 --> 00:20:05.190
And Abraham staggered not at the promise

00:20:05.200 --> 00:20:07.669
of God through unbelief, but was strong

00:20:07.679 --> 00:20:09.990
in faith, giving glory to God, being

00:20:10.000 --> 00:20:13.750
fully persuaded that what he had been

00:20:13.760 --> 00:20:16.150
promised, he was able also to perform

00:20:16.160 --> 00:20:19.430
it. Ladies and gentlemen, we have to be

00:20:19.440 --> 00:20:22.310
fully persuaded that God is a God

00:20:22.320 --> 00:20:25.110
of abundance. God is a healer.

00:20:25.120 --> 00:20:27.350
God is a God of love. We have to be

00:20:27.360 --> 00:20:29.350
fully persuaded. But he brings things

00:20:29.360 --> 00:20:31.750
and he wants you to intercede on behalf

00:20:31.760 --> 00:20:33.510
of America.

00:20:33.520 --> 00:20:35.350
What did Jesus tell me when I had the

00:20:35.360 --> 00:20:38.950
visitation? He said, "Brandon, who will

00:20:38.960 --> 00:20:42.470
stand in the gap for America? Who will

00:20:42.480 --> 00:20:45.110
intercede for America for what's

00:20:45.110 --> 00:20:45.120
coming?"I

00:20:45.120 --> 00:20:47.270
told you, ladies and

00:20:47.280 --> 00:20:50.390
gentlemen, there is a great storm.

00:20:50.400 --> 00:20:53.830
Sobering days are coming. But I believe

00:20:53.840 --> 00:20:55.909
as believers, we have power and

00:20:55.919 --> 00:20:57.909
authority to tread on serpents and

00:20:57.919 --> 00:21:00.630
scorpions, and nothing shall by any

00:21:00.640 --> 00:21:03.029
means hurt us. I believe with all my

00:21:03.039 --> 00:21:04.870
heart that we can speak to the mountain

00:21:04.880 --> 00:21:06.630
and tell it to be removed and be thou

00:21:06.640 --> 00:21:08.710
cast in the sea if we shall not doubt in

00:21:08.720 --> 00:21:11.270
our hearts. I believe you shall have

00:21:11.280 --> 00:21:14.549
whatsoever things you say because faith

00:21:14.559 --> 00:21:17.510
comes by hearing and hearing by the word

00:21:17.520 --> 00:21:19.669
of God. And as you get that word down

00:21:19.679 --> 00:21:21.750
inside of you and renew your mind every

00:21:21.760 --> 00:21:23.669
day,

00:21:23.679 --> 00:21:25.270
life and death is in the power of your

00:21:25.280 --> 00:21:27.669
tongue. And what you say out of your

00:21:27.679 --> 00:21:29.029
mouth, you're going to start living

00:21:29.039 --> 00:21:31.750
tomorrow. What you said out of your mouth

00:21:31.760 --> 00:21:33.909
yesterday, you're living today. I'm

00:21:33.919 --> 00:21:36.390
telling you, the fruit of what you say

00:21:36.400 --> 00:21:38.549
is what you're going to start living

00:21:38.559 --> 00:21:40.390
because that's what the Bible says. Life

00:21:40.400 --> 00:21:43.430
and death is in the power of the tongue.

00:21:43.440 --> 00:21:44.710
You're going to start living it. Ladies

00:21:44.720 --> 00:21:45.990
and gentlemen, if you start speaking

00:21:46.000 --> 00:21:47.430
blessing over your life instead of

00:21:47.440 --> 00:21:49.270
curses, you're going to start living

00:21:49.280 --> 00:21:51.430
a blessed life. I believe it. An

00:21:51.440 --> 00:21:54.390
abundant life, an overflow life, a life

00:21:54.400 --> 00:21:56.230
full of prosperity and health and

00:21:56.240 --> 00:21:58.630
healing and wellness for your family.

00:21:58.640 --> 00:22:00.230
But you start cursing your husband and

00:22:00.240 --> 00:22:02.630
you say, "Oh, he's a

00:22:02.630 --> 00:22:02.640
